Airport Operator TAV Havalimanlari of Turkey Planning to Expand in Africa

-- B y   R o b e r t   B r a n d
-- 
2011-07-28T08:18:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/airport-operator-tav-havalimanlari-of-turkey-planning-to-expand-in-africa.html
TAV Havalimanlari Holding AS (TAVHL) ,
 Turkey ’s biggest airport operator, plans to expand in  Africa ,
Chief Executive Officer Sani Sener said.  TAV will “select locales” in well-governed African
countries, Sener said at a conference in Franschhoek, outside
 Cape Town , today. TAV will “definitely look at  South Africa .”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Robert Brand in Cape Town at 
 rbrand9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  